<br>
Tanth prefers (and I agree) HK because the smith bank and forge are all closer together and also indicated has any easier time getting buffed there to increase str int (or wis) there.   I did a bit of MQ folded smithing in steamfont and the trip from the windmills to the forge and bank gets old pretty quick. &lt;g&gt;<br>
<br>
With the costs involved in plate smithing I'd suggest picking a main base and trying to max your faction there - the savings at the merchant NPCs in the long run are well worth the investment of time.  <br>
<br>
Storgue<br>
